---
title: Shiitake Mushroom Ramen with Ginger-Leek Broth & Udon
description: Forget your college dorm ramen. This ramen is the real deal. An umami-packed broth gives this dish intense depth, while meaty shiitakes and briny seaweed add unexpected bursts of flavor. Warning: loud slurping may occur.
